reviews.review_text: FYI-Tracklisting on player is off by 1 Just a heads up that the tracklisting on the player is off by one.

89-09-29 Good sound as per usual with a C Miller remaster. Nowhere near as good of a show as many 1989 classics. IMO 

I would recommend these '89 shows: 5-7, 7-7, 7-9, 7-17, 7-18, 7-19, 8-5, 10-9, 10-23, 12-8, 12-9, 12-27, 12-28 and 12-31.
